Promotion/Relegation Playoffs

First Leg [Nov 14]
Maldonado   2-3 Rampla Juniors
  [F.Fajardo(RJ,2), D.Pereira(RJ), P.Cuello(DM), M.Barceló(DM)]

Second Leg [Nov 18]
Rampla Jrs. 1-3 Deportivo Maldonado
  [G.Matosas(RJ), M.Barceló(DM), M.Cortés(DM), M.Affonso(DM)]

Playoff [Nov 21, Estadio Centenario]
Rampla Jrs. 1-1 Deportivo Maldonado    [6-5 pen]
  [M.Barceló(DM), R.Aguerre(RJ)]
  [penalties: 
   Pereira, Badell, Pappa, Perdomo, Kanapkis, Aguerre scored for Rampla.
   Márcora, Cortés, Giménez, Aldao, Affonso scored for Deportivo.
   Seré(RJ) saved Cuello(DM)'s penalty.]
Rampla Juniors remain in first division.


